@node "INFO" "SN XFerTracker v1.2 - Information"
@toc "MAIN"
┌───────────────────────────────────┐
  SN XFerTracker v1.2 - Information
└───────────────────────────────────┘

   Ever wonder who's downloaded a certain file?  I mean, you can tell how
many users have downloaded it, but WHO?  Ever wonder what files a certain
user has uploaded or downloaded?  Now you can keep track of all of the
above with SN XFerTracker!
   I have attempted to include everything this type of program needs, but
mine being the only SysOp's viewpoint, I have almost certainly left out a
certain feature someone wants or needs.  Please let me know of these and I
will do all I can to add this into the next release.

Features to note:
  - Self-cleaning.  Leaves no temp files lying around.
  - Mails you a nightly report on the day's uploads and downloads.
  - First time it's used, it does a date stamp and lets you and others
    know when it was installed.  (i.e. no history before this date.)

───SN/AHI (910) 326-3804 (28.8k)─────────────────────────────────────────
@endnode
