@node "BUGS" "SN XFerTracker v1.2 - Bugs/Problems"
@toc "MAIN"
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
  SN XFerTracker v1.2 - Bugs/Problems
└─────────────────────────────────────┘

  - This isn't a bug, but rather a drawback to this version that will
    hopefully be cleared up in the future:  It only works for UDBase0:
    If you're using more than that, it won't track correctly.

  - No known bugs at this point.  Please contact me if you do manage
    to trap one.  Thanks.

